body_html:
Thanks for the clarification and the instructions. As you can see, I'm a
Tensorflow noob. You're right that everything shows up as expected now
and I'm really puzzled why it does since I changed nothing in the
graph/scalars or images but it seems to be working fine. I'm obviously
mocking things up here and there but I have no idea how; in other words,
I'm quite dangerous at this stage since I clearly don't know enough how
to operate Tensorflow.

Thanks for you help

files you uploaded, there are no scalar summaries (and --inspect
confirms that). So something has changed since you posted this issue.
